{"title":"故乡诗抄","authors":["凌翼"],"dates":[{"year":2001,"month":3,"day":29}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"故乡诗抄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凌翼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冬笋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"告别故乡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乡亲送我一篮子冬笋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚下的路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是故乡延伸过来的一根长长竹鞭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一直追踪我到异乡的家门口"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当这根竹鞭发芽出笋时"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我又踩着思乡的脚步"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一路挖回去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吊桥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两个村庄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中间隔着一条河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一对相恋的人  隔河相望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当相思的茧不断绕大"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天长地久后"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"茧里抽出了钢丝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两个村庄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"砍来各自的木头锯成木板"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铺在钢丝上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就有了现在这座桥"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}